 Yervand Garginian , a 60-year-old bus driver from South Croydon in Melbourne , filmed himself cooking chicken on an open charcoal barbecue using a traditional ` khorovats ' recipe at a recent family gathering .
In the video Mr Garginian moved to Australia from Armenia in 1977 , dismisses the Australian-style barbecue of cooking ` oily ' sausages .
His daughter Elizabeth posted the video to Reddit and it has been viewed more than five million times after it was shared across Facebook , YouTube and Instagram .